---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Money Back Guarantee*.">
  <section class="page-intro">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>Short songs. Loud amps. Good bad ideas.</h1>
    <p>
      Money Back Guarantee* is a band built around sharp guitars, elastic rhythm
      sections, and the kind of choruses that sound slightly dangerous live.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="two-column">
    <article class="panel">
      <p class="eyebrow">Bio</p>
      <p>
        Start with post-punk edges, add power-pop instincts, then drag the whole
        thing through house-show PAs and late-night demo sessions. That is the
        shape of the band.
      </p>
      <p>
        Use this page for the final press bio, member lineup, booking contact,
        and downloadable assets once you have them ready.
      </p>
    </article>
    <article class="panel accent-panel">
      <p class="eyebrow">Contact</p>
      <p>Booking: booking@moneybackguaranteeband.com</p>
      <p>Press: press@moneybackguaranteeband.com</p>
      <p>General: hello@moneybackguaranteeband.com</p>
    </article>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
